<HEADLINE>
WALL TO GET KICKS AT USC
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ Birmingham High School kicker John Wall has
accepted a USC football scholarship.
</P>
<P>
   Wall, a two-time all-Daily News kicker who had 26 career field
goals, originally had signed a letter of intent to play at San Jose
State, but the Spartans wanted Wall to walk on his first semester.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-06-02-00 0126EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT20000602.0033 </DOCNO>
