   &UR; QUIPS, QUIRKS AND QUOTES FROM THE CAMPAIGN TRAIL &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; CAMPAIGN-TRAIL-MIX-ECONOMIST &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Political, Commentary, Humor Editors) &QL;
