<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR; LEBANON-REFUGEES (Doheria, Lebanon) _ With the Israeli
pullback from south Lebanon, hope for Palestinian refugees to
return to their ancestral homeland has been dramatically rekindled.
