Vladimir Putin on a variety of issues, including nuclear weapons
reductions. But in the weeks and days leading up to the summit, the
Clinton administration has greatly reduced its aspirations about
what the meetings will produce. Developing. Wraps in developments
from Germany. Will wrap in daily developments. (Deans, Cox News
Service).
