preparation for the Democratic National Convention in August. The
department head quoted in the Los Angeles Daily News issued a
statement repudiating his comments to the newspaper, which
witnesses say he also made earlier during a meeting. By Rick Orlov.
(Will move in the ``a'' national and ``n'' California state news
files.)
