 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    PUETO RICAN HOTSPOT: VIEQUES. Hoteliers are eyeing Vieques as a
hot new tourist destination _ that is, if Puerto Ricans can evict
the U.S. Navy.
 &HT;    Filed as BC-VIEQUES-TOURISM-LATINTRADE-NYTSF in ``f'' financial,
``l'' lifestyle, ``t'' travel.
