<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-02 21:11 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3298 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-STOCKS-ASSESS-ART-NYT     06-02 0890
