<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-02 21:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3316 &Cx1f; taf-z
s f BC-SOFTWARE-SCOTUS-ART-$     06-02 1353
